verbose_text: As regards the underlying the molecular mechanisms, as shown in XREF_FIG, AIV treatment significantly increased the Bcl-2, Bcl2 / Bax and FasL protein expression levels, which were downregulated by HG in the RPE cells in vitro, and significantly decreased the Bax, Fas, Fas / FasL, active caspase-3, active caspase-8 and active caspase-9 protein expression levels, which were upregulated by HG in the RPE cells.
